data.description: Assumable VA mortgage with great rate available. This expansive 2-story home offers a wealth of features that create a comfortable and convenient living environment. With 5 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, it provides plenty of space for any buyer looking to spread out. The wood-like laminate flooring throughout the house adds a touch of warmth and elegance, while the designated office space is perfect for those who work from home or need a dedicated workspace. One of the notable features of this home is its SMART capabilities. The home is prewired with commercial grade equipment for Wi-Fi, with signal extenders on both floors. The kitchen is a highlight, featuring elegant granite countertops, an oversized breakfast bar, plenty of cabinet storage, and a stylish subway tile backsplash. The stainless steel appliances add both functionality and a modern touch to the space. For added privacy, the primary bedroom is located downstairs. It includes an ensuite bathroom with a fully tiled walk-in shower, double vanities for convenience, and an expansive walk-in closet to accommodate your wardrobe and belongings. Upstairs, you'll find four additional bedrooms, each with easy access to two full bathrooms. The second living space is a versatile bonus area, perfect for a game room, movie nights, or entertaining guests.  Stepping outside, the backyard space is delightful, featuring a covered patio that provides an excellent spot for relaxation and enjoying the outdoors. The automatic sprinkler system helps maintain a green and lush lawn throughout the year, with minimal effort. The Wortham Oaks Community offers controlled access for added security and various amenities, including a community pool, park, and playground, promoting a great atmosphere. The home's location near retail shopping, entertainment, and eateries adds to its appeal, providing easy access to everyday conveniences and recreational options. Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough.
